WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:08.479
Hello!

00:00:09.754 --> 00:00:10.700
How are you?

00:00:20.737 --> 00:00:23.733
I believe this is a very thrilling
moment for them,

00:00:24.441 --> 00:00:28.932
just a few people have the chance
to meet a professional player,

00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:30.306
who they usually see on TV.

00:00:30.905 --> 00:00:32.195
I'm saying this
based on my son,

00:00:32.196 --> 00:00:33.690
when he goes to the stadium
he keeps staring at the players,

00:00:33.691 --> 00:00:35.913
then he asks me
several questions about them,

00:00:35.914 --> 00:00:39.375
how they are,
personally speaking,

00:00:39.376 --> 00:00:41.627
and when he's next to them
he just stands still,

00:00:41.628 --> 00:00:43.670
kind of shy,

00:00:43.671 --> 00:00:44.671
kind of introverted.

00:00:44.672 --> 00:00:45.890
This is really cool,

00:00:46.476 --> 00:00:49.684
and it's important to show
them that, despite...

00:00:50.005 --> 00:00:52.619
our artistic side
shown on TV,

00:00:52.620 --> 00:00:55.257
we're still kids,

00:00:55.386 --> 00:00:56.862
the kid inside of us never dies.

00:00:56.863 --> 00:00:59.661
It's great to be a part of this,
to be able to hug them,

00:00:59.662 --> 00:01:01.246
to take pictures,
to give autographs,

00:01:01.386 --> 00:01:03.320
and to give them
a moment of joy.

00:01:10.693 --> 00:01:12.663
I was a kid once,

00:01:12.664 --> 00:01:15.777
and I used to be very happy
whenever I met a player,

00:01:16.209 --> 00:01:20.604
and I believe this is a
dream come true to them.

00:01:21.107 --> 00:01:23.121
I wish they manage
to achieve their goals,

00:01:23.227 --> 00:01:24.777
may God bless their lives,

00:01:25.066 --> 00:01:28.514
and I hope they managed to achieve
their goals, as well as we are.

00:01:39.573 --> 00:01:42.536
It's great to receive affection,
specially from children.

00:01:43.275 --> 00:01:44.521
I'm still a kid,

00:01:44.522 --> 00:01:45.515
despite my age,

00:01:46.539 --> 00:01:47.415
always...

00:01:49.248 --> 00:01:53.114
may we always have
the heart of a child,

00:01:53.755 --> 00:01:55.068
that's where true integrity is.

00:01:56.163 --> 00:01:58.978
I can only thank them for coming,
God bless all of them.

00:02:04.231 --> 00:02:05.797
Their presence here
was very important,

00:02:05.798 --> 00:02:09.518
they motivated our boys to...

00:02:10.183 --> 00:02:13.833
keep working hard
on their daily training sessions,

00:02:14.174 --> 00:02:15.395
it was great.

00:02:15.396 --> 00:02:19.475
Even the adults...

00:02:19.872 --> 00:02:22.236
wanted to take pictures with
their idols, imagine the children.

00:02:22.237 --> 00:02:24.190
We ran a raffle at the franchise,

00:02:24.191 --> 00:02:26.327
and 10 out of 50 boy...

00:02:26.328 --> 00:02:28.114
came here today.

00:02:28.115 --> 00:02:30.676
It was a great initiative
promoted by Santos FC,

00:02:30.677 --> 00:02:33.240
which gathered...

00:02:33.241 --> 00:02:36.647
all these children from Londrina
who support Santos FC.

